* As seen by the developer

* Programmable global infrastructure

.image ethereum/whitespace.png

Nodes run a custom [[https://ethereum.github.io/yellowpaper/paper.pdf][virtual machine]]

- Stack-based *bytecode* interpreter â‡” multiple higher level languages
- Transactions are VM *executions* â‡’ transfer, then *run* available code
- Transactions carry *data* payload â‡’ user input and code deployment

.image ethereum/whitespace.png

Resource consumption and the halting problem

- Programs run in *varying* time â‡” fees based on VM *instructions*
- Complexity up to *infinite* loops â‡” *capped* maximum resource use

